docs.text: General medical datasets # OpenNeuro # OpenNeuro : A free and open platform for sharing MRI, MEG, EEG, iEEG, ECoG, and ASL data. The Cancer Imaging Archive # The Cancer Imaging Archive ( TCIA ): is a service which de-identifies and hosts a large archive of medical images of cancer accessible for public download. You can also Submit Your Data, Many TCIA datasets are submitted by the user community. US Governemnet Data # US gov data : The home of the U.S. Government’s open data, you will find data, tools, and resources to conduct research, develop web and mobile applications, design data visualizations. IEEE dataport # IEEE dataport : Easily store and access hundreds of datasets, including big data datasets, through IEEE's dataset storage and dataset search platform, DataPort. University of California Irvine dataset repository # University of California Irvine ( UCI ): UCI Machine Learning Repository. PhysioNet # PhysioNet : is a repository of freely-available medical research data, managed by the MIT Laboratory for Computational Physiology. EU Open Data Portal # The EU Open Data Portal : is the point of access to public data published by the EU institutions, agencies and other bodies. Information can be used and reused for commercial or non-commercial purposes. The portal is a key instrument of the EU open data strategy. Cambridge Centre for Ageing and Neuroscience (Cam-CAN) # Cambridge Centre for Ageing and Neuroscience ( Cam-CAM ) data repository for (Cam-CAN) dataset can be found here Cam-CAN archive . Archer-Soft --> Health data # health data : dedicated to making high value health data more accessible to entrepreneurs, researchers, and policy makers in the hopes of better health outcomes for all. BROAD Institute Cancer Program Datasets # BROAD Institute Cancer Program Datasets : Google dataset research tool # Google dataset : The Google Cloud Public Datasets Program hosts copies of structured and unstructured data to make it easier for users to discover, access, and utilize public data ... Data World # Data world 's cloud-native data catalog makes it easy for everyone—not just the "data people"—to get clear, accurate, fast answers to any business question.
